        "setup": "In your Workday tenant, create an API client for the app using Workday's **Create Your API Client** flow in the developer docs at [Create Your API Client](https://developer.workday.com/documentation/zwx1518028675482). Workday states that its REST and Graph APIs use OAuth 2.0. Configure the client in your tenant and use the resulting client details to obtain access tokens for the tenant APIs.",
