        "setup": "Install WDCLI from the Workday developer docs page [Install the Workday Developer CLI for Integration Apps on Windows](https://developer.workday.com/documentation/GUID-e9313aa2-6877-4aa4-8cc6-d5f810a9e3cf-enHYPHENus/InstalltheWorkdayDeveloperCLIforIntegrationAppsonWindows) (the same docs tree also provides the macOS/Linux installers). For non-human automation, set up a system user account as described in [Set Up WDCLI System User Accounts for Integration Apps](https://developer.workday.com/documentation/GUID-e0ab67fe-9fbc-4b26-be06-4a947d800a5a-enHYPHENus/SetUpWDCLISystemUserAccountsforIntegrationApps). Then log in through WDCLI using that account rather than sharing a human user's credentials.",
